== Description ==

iNove theme inspired by MacZone.sk.
It is very stylish, widget supported and doesn’t require any plugin.

Current version is not compatible with WordPress 2.x.x, but you can download the previous version on http://www.neoease.com/themes/

Tested on WordPress 3.0, with IE 6/7/8, Firefox 3.6, Opera 10.5, Safari 4 and Chrome 5.0.
Valid XHTML 1.1 and CSS 3!
Best view under 1024×768 or greater.

